<package version="1.0">
    <name>SQL_Query</name>
    <summary>
An OO-interface for easily retreiving and modifying a SQl-Query.
    </summary>

    <description>
This package provides an object oriented interface for building a SQL query.
It is aimed to provide all the functionality to build any query that can be sent
to a DB. Building the query means representing the query in an object.
For rendering the query into a string that can be sent to a DB SQL_Query_Renderer
is meant. This package will provide functionality to render a query defined using this
package for any kind of DB-backend.
    </description>

